Description: The package provides global envelopes with intrinsic graphical interpretation. They can be used for graphical Monte Carlo and permutation tests where the test statistic is a multivariate vector or function (e.g. goodness-of-fit testing for point patterns and random sets, functional ANOVA, functional GLM, n-sample test of correspondence of distribution functions), for central regions of functional or multivariate data (e.g. outlier detection, functional boxplot) and for global confidence and prediction bands (e.g. confidence band in polynomial regression, Bayesian posterior prediction). See Myllymäki et al. (2017) <doi: 10.1111/rssb.12172>, Mrkvička et al. (2017) <doi: 10.1007/s11222-016-9683-9>, Mrkvička et al. (2018) <arXiv:1612.03608>, Mrkvička et al. (2019) <arXiv:1906.09004>, Mrkvička et al. (2019) <arXiv:1902.04926>.
